title: 'Single' Selena Gomez scared of dating app Tinder
text:
Looks like Selena Gomez does not need the help of dating app Tinder to date guys, as she recently said she is "scared" to do so.
READ: How Justin Bieber gives 'goosebumps' to Selena Gomez?
The 23-year-old singer, who previously dated Justin Bieber, admitted going on dates with other boys. However, she said she would never use the app for dating, adding that she does not find it "difficult to meet guys" of her liking , The Mirror reports.
